From 1992 to 2003 the Wally Lewis Medal was awarded by the Queensland Rugby League for the Queensland player of the series .
Since 2003 it has been awarded to the player of the series , irrespective of state .
The following players have been awarded the Wally Lewis Medal for player of the series .
Cameron Smith has won the medal a record four times .
