UNDER 20S Section::::Under 20s .
The Under 20s State of Origin has only had seven seasons so far ( 2012 to 2018 ) with only one game a year , instead of three .
New South Wales has won six of the seven , with Queensland winning their first in 2018 .
They play for the Darren Lockyer Shield . !
