Section::::Women 's State of Origin .
The Women 's State of Origin is the Women 's rugby league version of the game , and has been running since 1999 .
The players play for the Nellie Doherty Cup .
Furthermore , the current record for series won in the competition rests with Queensland , who won every series from 1999 - 2014 , a better straight record than their male counterparts . !
